-- Mitchell, Barry (1965), Theory of categories, MR 0202787, p.12, Proposition 10.1
@[ext]
theorem image.ext [HasImage f] {W : C} {g h : image f ‚ü∂ W} [HasLimit (parallelPair g h)]
